║  Decentralized Memory OS for AI Agent Swarms       ║
║  Powered by 0G Storage + 0G Compute                ║
╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

Research Goal: "\ What is 0G Labs,how does decentralized AI storage work,and why does it matter for the future of AI in 2026\"

What will happen:
  1. Planner agent breaks goal into tasks → writes to 0G Storage
  2. Researcher agent executes tasks → writes facts to 0G Storage
  3. Critic agent reviews facts → updates confidence scores
  4. Reflection engine compresses memory via 0G Compute inference
  5. Final snapshot archived to 0G Storage Log permanently
  6. Restart with same SWARM_ID — swarm resumes from memory

